videos.description: South Carolina's Brea Beal blocks a shot on defense, grabs the rebound and goes coast-to-coast for an and-1 score.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Beal blocks shot, scores on other end for South Carolina) 2020/02/23

videos.headline: Beal blocks shot, scores on other end for South Carolina

videos.description: Ogechi Anyagaligbo catches the ball in the post and gets her defender to bite on a pump fake before finishing through contact for the hoop and the harm.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (UK's Anyagaligbo fools defender on and-1 bucket) 2020/02/23

videos.headline: UK's Anyagaligbo fools defender on and-1 bucket

videos.description: South Carolina guard Zia Cooke creates space with a crossover between her legs and drains the midrange jump shot.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Cooke knocks down smooth step-back jumper) 2020/02/23

videos.headline: Cooke knocks down smooth step-back jumper

videos.description: Zia Cooke hits a floater in transition, then comes up with a steal on defense and scores again for two baskets in less than 20 seconds.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Cooke cooks up back-to-back scores for South Carolina) 2020/02/23

videos.headline: Cooke cooks up back-to-back scores for South Carolina

videos.description: With the shot clock winding down, South Carolina's Aliyah Boston stuffs Jaida Roper's 3-point attempt to force the Kentucky turnover.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Boston's block forces Kentucky shot clock violation) 2020/02/23

videos.headline: Boston's block forces Kentucky shot clock violation
